<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>New Application Notification - Blue Sky</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f6f9;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #333;
    }
    .email-container {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 30px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: #fff;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 30px 20px;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 26px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 30px 40px;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .content h2 {
      color: #007bff;
      margin-top: 0;
    }
    .quote-box {
      background-color: #e7f1ff;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-left: 4px solid #007bff;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 14px;
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 15px;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Blue Sky</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p><strong>Hello <%= recruiter_name %>,</strong></p>

      <p>We wanted to inform you that a new candidate has applied for the position of <strong><%= job_title %></strong> at your company.</p>

      <div class="quote-box">
        <strong>Applicant Name:</strong> <%= applicant_name %><br/>
        <strong>Email:</strong> <%= applicant_email %><br/>
        <strong>Phone:</strong> <%= applicant_phone %><br/>
        <strong>Applied On:</strong> <%= application_date %>
      </div>

      <p>You can review the application and take further action through the portal.</p>

      <a href="<%= portal_url %>" class="btn">View Application</a>

      <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Thank you for using Blue Sky to manage your hiring process.</p>

      <p>Best regards,<br><strong>Blue Sky Recruitment Team</strong></p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Blue Sky. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
